name: Warmup_Div01_Sub04
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD1S4.CPF,
GmailD1S4.NOME,
GmailD1S4.EMAIL,
GmailD1S4.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S4.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD1S4.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD1S4.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S4.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV01_SUB04 GmailD1S4
UNION
